Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:53.61,op trans,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The fight doesn't end until I fulfill my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:59.87,op trans,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I wonder how far I've come now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:05.16,op trans,,0,0,0,,{\be1}In ten years, I'll be living the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:11.67,op trans,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's the scenario I wrote for myself, so I'll have no regrets
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:18.30,op trans,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But life isn't that easy, and it's full of obstacles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:24.64,op trans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,751)\be1}Still, I swear to myself that I won't ever back down
